dc_title_s: Pierhead and bulkhead lines for Hackensack River, N.J., from Newark and New York R.R. Bridge to Saw Mill Creek
dc_description_s: Map showing the pierhead and bulkhead lines of various business and private properties along the Hackensack River, from the Newark and New York Railroad Bridge to Saw Mill Creek. Also summarizes location of monuments with survey sketches.|Source map supplied by New Jersey Department of Environmental Protection|Drawn by W.B.M.|File No. Hack R. 1/63
